    <div id="status-tab" class="content-tab-panel">
            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>Any amendments to the guideline in the interim period will be noted on the <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180712195205/http://www.sign.ac.uk/new.html" title="SIGN Web site">Scottish Intercollegiate Guidelines Network (SIGN) Web site</a>.</p>
<p>This guideline meets NGC's 2013 (revised) inclusion criteria.</p></div></p>
    </div>
